originalText.text: I'm so grateful for this amazing experience!! I've had chronic problems with hip and ankle pain and I feel a thousand times better after doing a cupping and moxibustion session with Ying.  She is very sweet and made it her priority to ensure that I was comfortable during my session.  I really appreciate all the knowledge she gave me about healing my body! I would recommend Wellness Acupuncture to anyone who wants to improve their overall well being!!!
